{"title":"hexo+git page建站总结","uid":"2ee84dfef38ab2dca7794fab4f24e1d6","text":"建站流程：1.安装Hexo依赖软件 Node.js (建议使用12.0以上版本) Git 2.安装结果检验 打开Git Bash或者cmd node -v npm -v若正常显示出node和npm的版本 安装成功 3.安装淘宝镜像源在Git Bash中运行如下命令： npm in...","date":"2023-01-31T12:42:22.382Z","updated":"2023-01-31T12:32:59.999Z","comments":true,"path":"api/pages/建站总结.json","covers":null,"excerpt":"","content":"<h2 id=\"建站流程：\"><a href=\"#建站流程：\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"建站流程：\"></a>建站流程：</h2><h3 id=\"1-安装Hexo依赖软件\"><a href=\"#1-安装Hexo依赖软件\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"1.安装Hexo依赖软件\"></a>1.安装Hexo依赖软件</h3><ul>\n<li>Node.js (建议使用12.0以上版本)</li>\n<li>Git</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"2-安装结果检验\"><a href=\"#2-安装结果检验\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"2.安装结果检验\"></a>2.安装结果检验</h3><ol>\n<li>打开Git Bash或者cmd</li>\n<li>node -v</li>\n<li>npm -v<br>若正常显示出node和npm的版本 安装成功</li>\n</ol>\n<h3 id=\"3-安装淘宝镜像源\"><a href=\"#3-安装淘宝镜像源\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"3.安装淘宝镜像源\"></a>3.安装淘宝镜像源</h3><p>在Git Bash中运行如下命令：</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-bash\" data-language=\"bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\"><span class=\"token function\">npm</span> <span class=\"token function\">install</span> <span class=\"token parameter variable\">-g</span> cnpm <span class=\"token parameter variable\">--registry</span><span class=\"token operator\">=</span>https://registry.npm.taobao.org<span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\"><span></span></span></code></pre>\n<p>安装后查看当前版本命令：</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-bash\" data-language=\"bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\">cnpm <span class=\"token parameter variable\">-v</span><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\"><span></span></span></code></pre>\n<p>安装淘宝镜像源的目的:提高下载速度</p>\n<h3 id=\"4-安装Hexo-cli\"><a href=\"#4-安装Hexo-cli\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"4.安装Hexo-cli\"></a>4.安装Hexo-cli</h3><p>在Git Bash中执行如下命令安装Hexo客户端：</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-bash\" data-language=\"bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\">cnpm <span class=\"token function\">install</span> <span class=\"token parameter variable\">-g</span> hexo-cli<span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\"><span></span></span></code></pre>\n<p>查看Hexo版本：</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-bash\" data-language=\"bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\">hexo <span class=\"token parameter variable\">-v</span><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\"><span></span></span></code></pre>\n<h3 id=\"5-创建并初始化Blog文件\"><a href=\"#5-创建并初始化Blog文件\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"5.创建并初始化Blog文件\"></a>5.创建并初始化Blog文件</h3><p>管理员模式下在Git Bash中执行如下命令：</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-bash\" data-language=\"bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\">hexo init<span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\"><span></span></span></code></pre>\n<p>使用本地端口部署页面：</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-bash\" data-language=\"bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\">hexo s<span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\"><span></span></span></code></pre>\n<h3 id=\"6-将文件部署到github上\"><a href=\"#6-将文件部署到github上\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"6.将文件部署到github上\"></a>6.将文件部署到github上</h3><p>1.在github上新建库，库名必须和自己github的id相同<br><a href=\"pic1.png\">pic1</a></p>\n","count_time":{"symbolsCount":439,"symbolsTime":"1 mins."},"toc":"<ol class=\"toc\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E5%BB%BA%E7%AB%99%E6%B5%81%E7%A8%8B%EF%BC%9A\"><span class=\"toc-text\">建站流程：</span></a><ol class=\"toc-child\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-3\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#1-%E5%AE%89%E8%A3%85Hexo%E4%BE%9D%E8%B5%96%E8%BD%AF%E4%BB%B6\"><span class=\"toc-text\">1.安装Hexo依赖软件</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-3\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#2-%E5%AE%89%E8%A3%85%E7%BB%93%E6%9E%9C%E6%A3%80%E9%AA%8C\"><span class=\"toc-text\">2.安装结果检验</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-3\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#3-%E5%AE%89%E8%A3%85%E6%B7%98%E5%AE%9D%E9%95%9C%E5%83%8F%E6%BA%90\"><span class=\"toc-text\">3.安装淘宝镜像源</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-3\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#4-%E5%AE%89%E8%A3%85Hexo-cli\"><span class=\"toc-text\">4.安装Hexo-cli</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-3\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#5-%E5%88%9B%E5%BB%BA%E5%B9%B6%E5%88%9D%E5%A7%8B%E5%8C%96Blog%E6%96%87%E4%BB%B6\"><span class=\"toc-text\">5.创建并初始化Blog文件</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-3\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#6-%E5%B0%86%E6%96%87%E4%BB%B6%E9%83%A8%E7%BD%B2%E5%88%B0github%E4%B8%8A\"><span class=\"toc-text\">6.将文件部署到github上</span></a></li></ol></li></ol>"}